Xerox Office Products






			Welcome. You've reached the Xerox Office Products site.
			
			Please visit our home page at http://www.xerox.com/office.
			An office product to meet every need.
			There's a job waiting to get done.  A routine print job.  A walk-up copy of a single page.  A critical hundred-page report that needs to be printed in full color, faxed, and emailed halfway around the world.  Or one of the countless jobs that fall somewhere in between.  Whatever the task, Xerox has the widest range of office products and systems to help you get it done.  All with more speed, reliability, and value than you ever thought possible.
		




Copiers
		For more information on our fast and affordable copiers, please see the Xerox CopyCentre copiers site mapPrinters
		For more information on our color printers and black and white printers, please see the Xerox Phaser printersMultifunction
		For more information on our multifunction products which can print, copy, scan, and fax, please see the Xerox Phaser and WorkCentre multifunction printers

Add impact with color.
		Looking for affordable, yet brilliant color?  Xerox color printers, color copiers, and color multifunctions deliver.  With color, your business will benefit from one of the most effective business tools available.  Color adds impact to documents, helps readers retain information and gives your business a more professional look.  It commands attention -- and paired with Xerox value, makes perfect business sense.
		 




