^ Williams, Martyn (August 13, 2013). "Impact of Xerox character-substitution bug wider than thought". PCWorld. Retrieved March 22, 2015. 
^ "BBC News - Xerox to update scan software after switched number outcry". BBC News. Retrieved March 22, 2015. 
^ http://www.xerox.com/assets/pdf/ScanningQAincludingAppendixA.pdf
^ Stim, Richard (2006). Patent, Copyright & Trademark. Nolo. p. 388. ISBN 1-4133-0196-7. 
